  - m_Id: 542038851314397
    m_Localized: 'Chapter Gimmick: Lava Zone'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314398
    m_Localized: Obstacle Gimmick
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314399
    m_Localized: Element Synergy
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314400
    m_Localized: Combat Trial
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314401
    m_Localized: Skill Range
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314402
    m_Localized: Commander Skill
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314403
    m_Localized: Assassin Position
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314404
    m_Localized: Add Combat Member
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314405
    m_Localized: Arena Defense Deck
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314406
    m_Localized: Buff Zone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314407
    m_Localized: 'Each chapter has its unique gimmick.

      In Chapter 2, the Lava
      Zone <color=#0055FF>deals a certain amount of damage per second</color> when
      a character is positioned on it.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314408
    m_Localized: 'Obstacles <color=#0055FF>restrict</color> the movement of both
      characters and monsters,

      and characters cannot be placed on those tiles.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314409
    m_Localized: "When two or more characters with the <color=#0055FF>same element
      synergy</color> are placed, \nthe synergy effect is activated."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314410
    m_Localized: 'The Combat Trial is a dungeon where you can obtain <color=#0055FF>Growth
      Crystals.</color>

      Clearing certain stages <color=#0055FF>increases</color>
      the number of units you can deploy.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314411
    m_Localized: 'Some skills of characters and monsters display their <color=#0055FF>range</color>
      on the tiles when activated.

      Check the skill range and <color=#0055FF>strategically
      place</color> your characters.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314412
    m_Localized: 'You can <color=#0055FF>support battles</color> using Commander
      Skills.

      Clearing <color=#0055FF>chapters</color> will unlock additional
      Commander Skills.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314413
    m_Localized: 'Assassins move immediately to the <color=#0055FF>enemy''s rear</color>
      at the start of battle.

      Use them to target the enemy backline.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314414
    m_Localized: "If you clear a <color=#0055FF>specific stage</color> of \nthe Combat
      Trials, \nyou can deploy <color=#0055FF>one additional unit</color>."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314415
    m_Localized: 'In the Arena Defense Deck settings, you can place <color=#0055FF>obstacle
      walls</color>

      These walls can <color=#0055FF>influence enemy movement</color>,
      so be sure to use them strategically.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314416
    m_Localized: 'Certain stages feature buff zones that grant <color=#0055FF>buffs
      to characters.</color>

      The buff remains active as long as the character
      stays within the <color=#0055FF>buff zone.</color>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314417
    m_Localized: Summon Result
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314418
    m_Localized: Wall
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 542038851314419
    m_Localized: Access is currently unavailable.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
