    m_Localized: Tank
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 790123393310859
    m_Localized: High <color=#F75D32>Phys DEF</color>, effectively blocks attacks
      of Guardians and <color=#F75D32>Rangers</color>, but powerless agaist <color=#0047AB>Mages</color>
      who use magic attacks.
