  - m_Id: 2166638962008489
    m_Localized: Arcana
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008490
    m_Localized: <color=#F75D32>High Magic DEF</color>, reducing damage from <color=#F75D32>Mages</color>,
      but powerless against <color=#0047AB>Rangers</color> with physical attacks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008491
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008492
    m_Localized: High <color=#F75D32>Phys DEF</color>, effectively blocks attacks
      of Guardians and <color=#F75D32>Rangers</color>, but powerless agaist <color=#0047AB>Mages</color>
      who use magic attacks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008493
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008494
    m_Localized: Uses <color=#F75D32>magic attacks</color>, effectively hitting<color=#F75D32>Tanks</color>,
      but powerless agaist <color=#0047AB>Guardians</color> with high magic defense.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008495
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008496
    m_Localized: <color=#F75D32>Longest range</color> and <color=#F75D32>High ATK</color>,
      effectively hitting <color=#F75D32>Guardians</color>, but powerless against
      <color=#0047AB>Tanks</color> with high physical defense.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008497
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008498
    m_Localized: "<color=#F75D32>High ATK SPD</color> and <color=#F75D32>MOV SPD</color>,
      \nwith a short <color=#F75D32>Skill Cooldown.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008499
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Skill Cooldown Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008500
    m_Localized: Specialized in <color=#F75D32>healing, buffing, and debuffing</color>,
      this position focuses on strengthening allies or weakening enemies. Supporters
      have <color=#0047AB>low</color> base ATK and HP.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008501
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> Reduction.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008502
    m_Localized: Applies <color=#F75D32>additional damage </color> to the enemies
      when the character attacks
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008503
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Damage equal to <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> of
      ATK'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008504
    m_Localized: "Increases the character\u2019s <color=#F75D32>Phys DEF.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008505
    m_Localized: '{0}units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> increase of Phys
      DEF'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008506
    m_Localized: Generates a <color=#F75D32>shield</color> for the entire team equal
      to the team's average attack power for <color=#F75D32>10 seconds</color>.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008507
    m_Localized: '{0}units : A shield equal to <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b>
      of ATK'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008508
    m_Localized: Grants a character <color=#F75D32>immunity to all status effects</color>
      for a certain period of time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008509
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Immune for <b><color=#F75D32>{1}seconds</color></b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008510
    m_Localized: "Reduces the enemy\u2019s <color=#F75D32>Skill Cooldown Reduction
      Speed.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008511
    m_Localized: '{0}units : Reduction by <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008512
    m_Localized: "Boosts the character\u2019s <color=#F75D32>ATK SPD.</color>"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008513
    m_Localized: '{0} units : <b><color=#F75D32>{1}%</color></b> increase in ATK
      SPD'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008514
    m_Localized: '{0} Synergy Deployment Effect'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008515
    m_Localized: NONE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008516
    m_Localized: NONE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008517
    m_Localized: "\uC655\uAC00\uC758 \uB099\uC778\uC774 \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4.
      \uB178\uBE14\uB808\uC2A4 \uC131\uAD70\uC744 \uAC00\uC9C4 \uAE30\uC0AC\uB4E4\uC758
      \uD06C\uAE30\uAC00 {0}% \uC0C1\uC2B9\uD558\uACE0 \uACF5\uACA9\uB825\uC774 {1}%
      \uC0C1\uC2B9\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008518
    m_Localized: "\uADC0\uC871\uC758 \uC758\uBB34\uAC00 \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4.
      \uB178\uBE14\uB808\uC2A4 \uC131\uAD70\uC744 \uAC00\uC9C4 \uAE30\uC0AC\uB4E4\uC758
      \uCD1D\uCCB4\uB825\uC758 {0}%\uC5D0 \uD574\uB2F9\uD558\uB294 \uC274\uB4DC\uAC00
      \uC0DD\uC131\uB429\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008519
    m_Localized: "\uC5D8\uB9AC\uD2B8\uC758 \uC790\uC874\uC2EC\uC774 \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4.
      \uC804\uD22C \uC2DC\uC791 \uD6C4 {0}\uCD08\uAC04 CC \uD6A8\uACFC\uC5D0 \uBA74\uC5ED\uC774\uB429\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008520
    m_Localized: NONE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008521
    m_Localized: "\uC804\uC120\uC744 \uC720\uC9C0\uD558\uAE30 \uC704\uD55C \uB300\uC804\uCC28
      \uC9C0\uB8B0\uB97C \uC804\uC7A5\uC5D0 \uC124\uCE58\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4. \uC9C0\uB8B0\uC758
      \uACF5\uACA9\uB825\uC740 \uC131\uAD70\uC6D0\uB4E4\uC758 \uACF5\uACA9\uB825\uC5D0
      \uBE44\uB840\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008522
    m_Localized: "\uB2E4\uC591\uD55C \uD6A8\uACFC\uB97C \uC9C0\uB2CC \uBCF4\uAE09\uD488\uC744
      {0}\uCD08 \uB9C8\uB2E4 \uD68D\uB4DD\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4. \uBCF4\uAE09\uD488 \uC548\uC5D0
      \uB0B4\uC6A9\uBB3C\uC740 \uBB34\uC791\uC704\uB85C \uACB0\uC815\uB429\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008523
    m_Localized: "\uC804\uD22C \uD568\uC120\uC744 {0}\uCD08 \uB9C8\uB2E4 \uBD88\uB7EC\uB0B4
      \uD3EC\uACA9\uC73C\uB85C \uC804\uC7A5\uC744 \uCD08\uD1A0\uD654 \uC2DC\uD0B5\uB2C8\uB2E4.
      \uD3EC\uACA9\uC758 \uC704\uB825\uC740 \uC131\uAD70\uC6D0\uB4E4\uC758 \uACF5\uACA9\uB825\uC5D0
      \uBE44\uB840\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008524
    m_Localized: NONE
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008525
    m_Localized: "\uC131\uAD70\uC6D0\uB4E4\uC758 \uCCB4\uB825 \uC911 {0}%\uC744 \uD761\uC218\uD558\uC5EC
      \uC2A4\uC2A4\uB85C \uBD88\uD0DC\uC6C1\uB2C8\uB2E4. \uC2A4\uC2A4\uB85C \uBD88\uD0DC\uC6CC
      \uCD08\uC2E0\uC131 \uBAA8\uB4DC1\uB2E8\uACC4\uC5D0 \uB3CC\uC785\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008526
    m_Localized: "\uC131\uAD70\uC6D0\uB4E4\uC758 \uACF5\uACA9\uB825 \uC911 {0}%\uC744
      \uD761\uC218\uD558\uC5EC \uC2A4\uC2A4\uB85C \uBD88\uD0DC\uC6C1\uB2C8\uB2E4.
      \uC2A4\uC2A4\uB85C \uBD88\uD0DC\uC6CC \uCD08\uC2E0\uC131 \uBAA8\uB4DC 2\uB2E8\uACC4\uC5D0
      \uB3CC\uC785\uD569\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2166638962008527
