  - m_Id: 2945424275264015
    m_Localized: 'Water Synergy Mage

      Skill: <color=#F75D32>Summons an ice</color>
      in a certain area to attack enemies.

      Deals additional damage to <color=#F75D32>Fire
      Synergy</color> enemies.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264016
    m_Localized: 'Water Synergy Ranger

      Skill: Delivers a <color=#F75D32>powerful
      strike</color> to a single enemy.

      If the skill kills the enemy, the
      Skill Cooldown is <color=#F75D32>immediately reset.</color>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264017
    m_Localized: 'Dark Synergy Assassin

      Skill: Deals damage to a single enemy
      and applies silence for a short duration.

      *Silence: The enemy cannot
      use skills for a certain period.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264018
    m_Localized: 'Fire Synergy Supporter

      Skill: Increases the <color=#F75D32>ATK</color>
      of all allies for a certain period.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264019
    m_Localized: Nameless Star
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264020
    m_Localized: Destroyer of the Earth
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264021
    m_Localized: Purest Executioner
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264022
    m_Localized: Guardian of Solace
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264023
    m_Localized: Steel Will
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2945424275264024
    m_Localized: 'Fire Synergy Mage


      Skill : Launches a <color=#F75D32>Fire
      Energy Spell</color> in a 3x3 area.

      The spell scorches the ground, dealing
      <color=#F75D32>additional damage.</color>'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
